sliceDataset Transformation
sliceDataset Parameters

Add a sliceDataset transformation to a dataflow either in the dataflow editor, or directly in the JSON dataflow definition file.

To add a sliceDataset transformation in the dataflow editor, click .

This table describes the input parameters:

PARAMETER	REQUIRED?	VALUE
source	Yes	Node in the dataflow definition file that identifies the dataset that you want to slice.
mode	Yes	
fields	Yes	An array of names of the fields that you want to drop or select from the specified source node.
